| C12 | Capacitor | 0.47uF, 10V | 0402 | DVDD Output Decoupling |
| C3-C6 | Capacitor | 100pF | 0402 | Differential Filtering (Daisy Chain) |
| D1, D3 | TVS Diode | PESD5V0L2BTN | - | Daisy Chain ESD Protection |
